# MovieList — code quality (`src/`)

## Defensive UI

- Treat **poster, backdrop, runtime, rating**, and **empty lists** as possibly missing. Branch on **null/undefined** and empty collections before rendering.

## TypeScript

- **`strict`**. No **`any`**. Prefer explicit unions and narrowing.

## Imports

- **Axios** only from **`src/api/client.ts`** (consumers use **`movies.ts`** / hooks). **TMDB** access only through hooks → **`movies.ts`** → **`client.ts`**.
- API types from **`src/api/types.ts`**; navigation types from **`src/navigation/types.ts`**.

## File size

- Keep files focused. If a screen or module grows unwieldy, split **presentational** pieces into **`src/components/`** rather than inline mega-components — without inventing new top-level folders.
